                "input": "prompt",
                "title": "User prompt",
                "type": "string",
                "value": "Este correo es el resumen semanal de mi cuenta en Peerberry. Extrae los siguientes valores del cuerpo del mail:\n- Fecha fin periodo: el mail muestra \"Balance on [inicio] - [fin]\". Devuelve SOLO la fecha de FIN del periodo, en formato YYYY-MM-DD.\n- Interest income: el importe de intereses de la semana (número).\n- Deposit: importe depositado. Si no aparece, usa 0.\n- Withdrawals: importe retirado. Si no aparece, usa 0.\n- Invested funds: del bloque Portfolio.\n- Available balance: del bloque Portfolio.\nDevuelve solo los números sin símbolos de moneda."
              },
              {
                "input": "codeSandbox",
                "description": "Recommendation: OFF, The task is to extract and format specific values from email text. This is a content understanding task, not a data transformation task that requires programmatic processing or file manipulation.",
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "AUTO",
                  "OFF",
                  "ON"
                ],
                "value": "AUTO"
              },
              {
                "input": "webAccess",
                "description": "Recommendation: OFF, The user is extracting structured data from an email that is already provided as input. No additional web access is needed to parse the email content.",
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "AUTO",
                  "OFF",
                  "ON"
                ],
                "value": "AUTO"
              },
              {
                "input": "review",
